translations: v．表示轻蔑或不屑一顾的声音，类似于“呸”。
· She poohs at the idea of going to the party.
她对去参加聚会的想法嗤之以鼻。

phrs.translation: 小熊维尼（一卡通片名称）

sentences.sentence: Russia pooh-poohs all this. It worries that Kaliningrad may be left an energy island as Lithuania and its Baltic neighbours integrate their power grids with the rest of Europe's.
sentences.translation: 俄罗斯对这一切嗤之以鼻，它担心的是，若立陶宛及其波罗的海邻国的电网融入欧洲其他地区的电网，会使加里宁格勒成为能源孤岛。
